{"tid":1417921,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"連儂spray paint?","createTime":"2019-08-05T17:28:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T04:30:36.000Z","uid":277554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b51840277e65d30c411703febe75052983202ebd","tid":1417921,"uid":277554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:28:34.000Z","msg":"不如玩spray paint玩到好似連儂牆咁勁<br />\n難洗，周街都睇到，俾人拉應該唔會太大獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"865caac0717d3c7e850bef94f6baf9db4c46dc52","tid":1417921,"uid":140127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:29:12.000Z","msg":"對黑社會唔係一開波就打呀！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1417668\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1417668</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1fdb900eb4a777f9c60b1f69374643cd65e6027b","tid":1417921,"uid":164043,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:35:41.000Z","msg":"噴柒義士"},{"pid":"6038593a3147994ffd8350ecbcc4132f1910005d","tid":1417921,"uid":277554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:39:17.000Z","msg":"依家風頭火勢咁 <br />\n不如落力係文宣方面<br />\n齊齊spray paint<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0de166542df541432ddfe516aacc81dee21e221","tid":1417921,"uid":24776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:40:32.000Z","msg":"其實塗鴉拉到嘅話會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 應該唔使坐掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30c9e9ffab671864d6057c55d5943e6ed0ff90c8","tid":1417921,"uid":277554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:42:59.000Z","msg":"連儂牆由一部牆延伸做一條隧道（大埔），連儂商場（新城市），連儂人，連儂長輩圖都出埋。<br />\n我覺得spray paint都可以玩盡佢。"},{"pid":"5025b6407b06b8b1e8cb2c4c3f8543cac4d99e69","tid":1417921,"uid":277554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0de166542df541432ddfe516aacc81dee21e221","tid":1417921,"uid":24776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:40:32.000Z","msg":"其實塗鴉拉到嘅話會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 應該唔使坐掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:15:30.000Z","msg":"在香港公眾地方或私人財產上塗鴉違法<br />\n<br />\n根據香港法例第 228 章《簡易程序治罪條例》：<br />\n<br />\n第4條19節，在任何公眾地方之內或附近，以雕刻或其他方式，將任何字母、字樣、數字或圖案標記在任何石頭或路塹上，以致其外觀受損，可處罰款$500或監禁3個月；若屬意圖摧毀或損壞該財產，而無合理理由等，或會列為「刑事毀壞」案件處理，一經定罪，最高可處監禁10年。<br />\n<br />\n第8條，沒有擁有人或佔用人同意下，任何人不得以粉筆或漆油在任何建築物或牆壁上書寫或留下記號，或將之弄污或毀損其外觀。<br />\n<br />\n早年曾有青年多次在港鐵和商場塗鴉和刮花玻璃，被法庭控告18項刑事毀壞罪名，判處220小時的社會服務令，並需向受影響單位賠償和清理，香港著名的塗鴉代表「九龍皇帝」曾灶財亦曾被多次檢控。"},{"pid":"9a8a051d12828658180a74d73b50935ce1db2fe8","tid":1417921,"uid":277554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:58:16.000Z","msg":"推到噴漆塗鴉普及化，外媒爭相報導<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7109a0d5b7217061568b8d4f46ce9c1ceeaf916f","tid":1417921,"uid":24776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:52:46.000Z","msg":"希望巴打做嘢嘅時候有多啲人一齊行動，因為班仆街藍絲會兜口兜面影鳩你，而你兇返佢嘅時候就話你想打佢，所以多人行動好啲，一切小心！！"},{"pid":"c603bb7705859516f530ef0364450d3318feece6","tid":1417921,"uid":277554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T04:30:36.000Z","msg":"最好一小隊一小隊人咁夜晚行動。<br />\n工具唔多，應該唔易捉到既。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}